caption.title: Extent of county subdivisions within the area analyzed.
caption.p: Each county subdivision (outlined in brown) is located within the analysis extent. In the analyzed area, the 100-yr flood risk area is displayed in yellow (baseline), orange (flood height accounting for the mean sea-level projection), red (flood height accounting for the Heberger et al. [ 7] sea-level projection; not accounting for land storage changes), and dark red (flood height accounting for sea-level rise uncertainty). The star represents the location of the tide gauge.
